  "response": "To recover your WeChat ID, you can try the following methods:\n\n1. Check Chat History\n- Open WeChat\n- Look through your existing chats\n- Your ID might be visible in previous conversations\n\n2. Check Profile Settings\n- Go to \"Me\" section\n- Tap on your profile photo\n- Your WeChat ID should be displayed there\n\n3. Contact WeChat Support\n- If you can't find your ID through these methods\n- Contact WeChat customer service for assistance\n\n4. Use Linked Phone Number/Email\n- If your account is linked to a phone number or email\n- You might be able to recover your ID through those\n\nNote: If you've completely lost access to your account, you may need to contact WeChat support directly for further help.",
